{"tid":1252990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【豆腐渣中資大樓】柬埔寨冧樓增至42死傷 疑有中國工人被困","createTime":"2019-06-23T10:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T07:57:00.000Z","uid":254183,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"124137b88e79e431493b69765581e0e191f7cebf","tid":1252990,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:18:52.000Z","msg":"柬埔寨一座興建中的中資大樓昨晨5時許倒塌，截至今日上午11時30分，已增至18人死亡、24人受傷，均為柬埔寨當地工人。當地1名黃姓華人說：「除了柬埔寨當地工人，還有中國工人在裏面。」華文媒體《柬中時報》證實「有中國人被困廢墟」，但因仍在搜救，當局未透露被困者的資訊。<br />\n西哈努克省政府針對塌樓事故發出的聲明指，事發地盤的4名負責人已接受警方問話，當中包括3名外籍業主及承包商。柬埔寨國土規劃和建設部發言人盛洛指，倒塌的7層高建築物佔地面積為450平方米，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">工程已完成約80%，但沒有申請「施工許可證」。</span></strong><br />\n中國駐柬埔寨大使館商務處昨日緊急通知西哈努克省中方企業，參與西哈努克市塌樓救援工作。中國駐柬商務處表示，目前中建二局已援助20箱礦泉水，安排1部大型挖掘機、3輛泥頭車、50名救援人員、10名管理人員參與救援。<br />\n柬埔寨警方則指，至少有1,000多名救援人員前往救援，他們估計至少需要2天徹底搜救。柬埔寨警方在聲明中表示，相信會有更多的倖存者出現，「因為救援正在進行，所以我們還不知道還有多少人被困。」<br />\n西哈努克省省長潤明透露，事發時這處建築地盤中大約40至50人正在正作，目前救援仍在進行中，估計傷亡人數會增加。目前，柬埔寨政府決定對死者的家屬給予1萬美元（約7.8萬港元）賠償、免除所有傷者醫療費用，並給予1,226美元（約9,615港元）的援助金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190623/59749161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190623%2F59749161&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=cdd09bad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190623%2F59749161&h=d628e5c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190623/59749161</a><br />\n<br />\n一帶一路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85c525fd2715aac7273649a5efc1a777487c014","tid":1252990,"uid":37501,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:25:13.000Z","msg":"蘋果最近日日吹奏柬埔寨既樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf016a3d98b5ca221fa740b8ac9c88760c027702","tid":1252990,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:33:30.000Z","msg":"一帶一露 建設美好將來<br />\n一帶到入其他國家就露曬餡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df1687d00e2196746927e57565fded0c7310173","tid":1252990,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:34:10.000Z","msg":"一帶一露<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff58f00b1969b29f61d15323f28a4ba05f938af","tid":1252990,"uid":84581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:35:43.000Z","msg":"&quot;柬埔寨政府決定對死者的家屬給予1萬美元（約7.8萬港元&quot;<br />\n<br />\n人命何價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce3edc1462913d60c6da035753f72fec628331d","tid":1252990,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:43:29.000Z","msg":"共享祖國光榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0090e4043f0f76a423e5d24c8bc735a17f6d8bc8","tid":1252990,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aabd4745bf7a4cd6e1c8788f48ca168219167469","tid":1252990,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:59:38.000Z","msg":"厲害了祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdfcb0ef9286955bd804d98a4b55008f201d137","tid":1252990,"uid":164184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"都2019年啦仲會話咁易就冧樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/